items.summary: Lots of people like this place

items.text: Best kebap in town.
Dünyanın en uzun döner kuyruğu ama beklemeye deger!
Die 20 Minuten die man hier auf seinen Döner wartet sind es definitiv wert !!
Dont waste your time, so NOT worth to wait for an hour in the line.
Try the running gag: "i want a vegetarian whatever wit meat."
Chicken Döner with fried vegetables and cottage cheese! Lecker!!
Every waiting time, even if it is 1 hour. Is worth it!
Der beste Döner in Berlin!
A different take on kebap with chicken, fresh veggies, and feta. Definitely worth the wait!
eine Stunde warten, aber der beste Kebap überhaupt
The Döner isn't bad but by far not that special to justify 30+ minutes cuing for it!
Nothing special just a hyped kebab ..
Go here when it's rainy. Queuing up is for tourists.
Am besten kurz nach Mittag kommen, da ist die Schlange noch kurz.
The secret is in the herbs: fresh mint in the salad, dill (?) on the cheese!
Its good but the hype is retarded, not worth more than a 15 minute wait
So here's the deal - I read the 4sq tips and saw the ratings first... Then waited in line like you all told me to for 20 minutes. It's SO worth the wait!!! Seriously we got two Dorems each.
Worth the wait.
Gemüsekebap
Best of kebap!!!

items.name: Berlin's best food
items.description: from the best snacks to the more expensive options in town - it's all on the list!

sample.text: Das warten lohnt sich, der döner war Top!

... und empfehlenswert:) die Schlange ist total lange :D
